{"TopicId":174061,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Deploy Kerbal Chute in Seat","CreatedByName":"HB Stratos","CreatedById":187428,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-18T18:49:21Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"HB Stratos","CreatedById":187428,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-18T18:49:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi everyone,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndo you know any way to deploy a kerbals chute in an external command seat?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any way to get it done (a mod, module manager script, etc)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwould be great for a project...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks in advance\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHb_Stratos\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Noobton","CreatedById":114094,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-18T19:09:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi Stratos, I moved your question to gameplay questions as I feel it might get better visibility here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t used the external seat outside of rovers so I can\u0027t help you there though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-19T14:06:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA command seat should be able to deploy a craft\u0027s parachutes without a mod under any circumstances.\u00A0 They along with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E are purely mechanical things which don\u0027t need power to function.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you mean the EVA parachute, that\u0027s a mod and should be in modded questions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-19T14:08:20Z\u0022 title=\u002204/19/2018 02:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 19, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Corona688\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HB Stratos","CreatedById":187428,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-19T14:12:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi Corona688,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean the eva chute so you can glide.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt was originally in KSP Discussion until noobton moved it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cpt Kerbalkrunch","CreatedById":175588,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-19T14:45:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223358543\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174061\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221524146778\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00222511\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Corona688\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n37 minutes ago, Corona688 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you mean the EVA parachute, that\u0027s a mod and should be in modded questions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbal personal parachutes we\u0027re included in the 1.4 update. So they\u0027re stock now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Noobton","CreatedById":114094,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-19T15:09:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223358548\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174061\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221524147133\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187428\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HB Stratos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n56 minutes ago, HB Stratos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi Corona688,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean the eva chute so you can glide.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt was originally in KSP Discussion until noobton moved it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\noops I thought it was regular chutes... rereorganizing it to the modded questions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpannerMonkey(smce)","CreatedById":50907,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-19T15:22:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223358576\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174061\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221524150540\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114094\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Noobton\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Noobton said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\noops I thought it was regular chutes... rereorganizing it to the modded questions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis isnt\u0027t a modded game question as the question is relevant if all you have is a bone stock game.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe 1.4 version added personal parachutes, no mods needed ,\u00A0 and so far ( as far as i know)\u00A0 there\u0027s no way to trigger the chute while sitting in a cmd chair,\u00A0 this is because technically the kerb is sitting in a pod\u00A0 IVA when he uses the cmd seat.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s either a gameplay question or a question for the addon discussions , certainly doesn\u0027t belong in a\u00A0 troubleshooting section for modded games.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Noobton","CreatedById":114094,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-19T15:32:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223358583\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174061\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221524151376\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250907\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpannerMonkey(smce)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, SpannerMonkey(smce) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis isnt\u0027t a modded game question as the question is relevant if all you have is a bone stock game.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe 1.4 version added personal parachutes, no mods needed ,\u00A0 and so far ( as far as i know)\u00A0 there\u0027s no way to trigger the chute while sitting in a cmd chair,\u00A0 this is because technically the kerb is sitting in a pod\u00A0 IVA when he uses the cmd seat.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s either a gameplay question or a question for the addon discussions , certainly doesn\u0027t belong in a\u00A0 troubleshooting section for modded games.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou are right, rerereorganizing it, shouldn\u0027t move stuff around before my morning coffee.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gordon Fecyk","CreatedById":157121,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-19T16:06:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHazard-ish managed to take advantage of 1.4 EVA chutes in a command seat. Something to do with deploying the chute and quickly entering the command seat.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/sSztXqAFtZ0?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HB Stratos","CreatedById":187428,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-20T19:29:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know but I was wondering if there was a reliable way to trick KSP and open the chute\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gordon Fecyk","CreatedById":157121,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-28T03:39:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like KSP 1.4.3 introduced the capability of opening the EVA chute while seated in a command chair.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022float:none;background-color:transparent;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:monospace, monospace;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:pre-wrap;word-spacing:0px;\u0022\u003E=================================== v1.4.3 ============================================================\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022float:none;background-color:transparent;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:monospace, monospace;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:pre-wrap;word-spacing:0px;\u0022\u003E\u002B\u002B\u002B Improvements\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[...]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont face=\u0022Consolas\u0022\u003E\u003Cfont color=\u0022#b00000\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:left;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;word-spacing:0px;white-space:pre-wrap;float:none;background-color:transparent;\u0022\u003E* Added ability to deploy parachute when kerbal is in command seat so that players can create paragliders.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-28T06:05:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup. But it\u0027s a lifting surface, not a control surface. So you need to add a full set of control surfaces.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Zeiss Ikon","CreatedById":174016,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-28T13:08:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223365912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174061\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221524895551\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup. But it\u0027s a lifting surface, not a control surface. So you need to add a full set of control surfaces.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, when used normally, i.e. goes EVA in atmosphere and left the vessel, the Kerbal is controlling the thing with weight shift?\u00A0 Because it certainly seems there\u0027s considerable pitch and roll/yaw (coupled) authority when flying a parachuting Kerbal.\u00A0 Weight shift would explain \u0022Their Legs Move!!\u0022 video...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-28T13:09:21Z\u0022 title=\u002204/28/2018 01:09  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 28, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Zeiss Ikon\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Draalo","CreatedById":158993,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-29T10:42:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/gYWuG7xzM1M?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}